fulltitle: The Sound of Ben Webster: Part Three
title: The Sound of Ben Webster: Part Three

http_headers.User-Agent: Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/74.0.3691.0 Safari/537.36

description: This episode of the National Jazz Museum in Harlem's series on Ben Webster does a deep dive into the magical years Ben spent with Duke Ellington and his band. You'll many rare items, including Ben jamming on the clarinet, and a comparison between Webster and Charlie Parker.
